{"tid":24843,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔係冇試過！我唔係冇試過！","createTime":"2016-12-05T18:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T13:16:36.000Z","uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea79832eaaf2869c9339367f9addac6d20b3ca24","tid":24843,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"我唔係冇試過去追女仔，<br />\n示好之後連朋友都冇得做。<br />\n我唔係冇試過死心塌地鍾意一條女，<br />\n但換來既都係俾人搶走。<br />\n我唔係冇試過唔諗愛情，只係當對方係朋友，順其自然，本來好好地但就突然永久已讀不回。<br />\n我唔係冇試過只係純粹視對方係朋友，完完全全冇諗過額外野，對你都冇feel。只係你悶悶地想行下街，想搵你做下伴，換來係&quot;唔好打我主意&quot;...<br />\nwhat?我....我.....我都冇咁既意思。<br />\n唉。懶得解釋。留番啖氣暖肚算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發up風。"},{"pid":"1ca287e9358e047ef9e183fc6a43b58fe310ec3b","tid":24843,"uid":3421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"你收嗲啦"},{"pid":"66a1b6715cbc91a19c0732dc24411530eb443b59","tid":24843,"uid":39150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"你的樣子如何......."},{"pid":"20fd0490041fed825585afb7ed07cb234bbcac31","tid":24843,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"冷靜d照下鏡"},{"pid":"d4f74ee7f5179622b98c56bd35539e89c8d445d9","tid":24843,"uid":51520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T17:02:37.000Z","msg":"儲錢整到啲韓仔咁個樣 學返兩句尋尋尋<br />\n啲港女就出晒水啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39455423e73b73d362d4c40cb9c0e9758ceb5efb","tid":24843,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T13:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}